						</header> <!-- end article header -->
					
						<section class="post_content">
						
							<!---->
						
							<p>Although not a major version change this update is our largest yet (aside from the 2.0 upgrade) and brings about some highly sought after features. Notable New Features: Post Meta Field Improvements Synced/Auto Populated Post Meta fields are now auto populated / synced. For choice fields this means you no longer have to manually enter the&#8230;  <a href="https://www.designsandcode.com/33533/search-filter-2-1-released/" class="more-link" title="Read Search &#038; Filter Pro 2.1 Released">Read more &raquo;</a></p>
					
						</section> <!-- end article section -->
						
						<footer>
							
						</footer> <!-- end article footer -->
					
					</article> <!-- end article -->
					
										
										
					<article id="post-25518" class="clearfix post-25518 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-uncategorized" role="article">
						
						<header>
							
							<h3 class="h2"><a href="https://www.designsandcode.com/25518/search-filter-2-0-released/" rel="bookmark" title="Search &#038; Filter Pro 2.0 Released!">Search &#038; Filter Pro 2.0 Released!</a></h3>
							
							<p class="meta">Posted <time datetime="2015-09-23" pubdate>9:43 am</time> by <a href="https://www.designsandcode.com/author/ross/" title="Posts by Ross" rel="author">Ross</a> <span class="amp">&</span> filed under <a href="https://www.designsandcode.com/category/uncategorized/" rel="category tag">Uncategorized</a>.</p>
						
						</header> <!-- end article header -->
					
						<section class="post_content">
						
							<!---->
						
							<p>So the time has finally come. About a year and half after our initial release we are ready to release v2.0 to the world. A lot has happened and a lot has changed &#8211; and the plugin has grown.. a lot. So before we start, I would like to again mention to all existing users to read&#8230;  <a href="https://www.designsandcode.com/25518/search-filter-2-0-released/" class="more-link" title="Read Search &#038; Filter Pro 2.0 Released!">Read more &raquo;</a></p>
					
						</section> <!-- end article section -->
						
						<footer>
							
						</footer> <!-- end article footer -->
					
					</article> <!-- end article -->
					
										
										
					<article id="post-720" class="clearfix post-720 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-cms category-css category-design category-development category-html category-javascript category-php category-plugins category-wordpress" role="article">
						
						<header>
							
							<h3 class="h2"><a href="https://www.designsandcode.com/720/search-filter-pro-wordpress-plugin/" rel="bookmark" title="Search &#038; Filter Pro for WordPress is out!">Search &#038; Filter Pro for WordPress is out!</a></h3>
							
							<p class="meta">Posted <time datetime="2014-05-14" pubdate>5:25 pm</time> by <a href="https://www.designsandcode.com/author/ross/" title="Posts by Ross" rel="author">Ross</a> <span class="amp">&</span> filed under <a href="https://www.designsandcode.com/category/cms/" rel="category tag">CMS</a>, <a href="https://www.designsandcode.com/category/css/" rel="category tag">CSS</a>, <a href="https://www.designsandcode.com/category/design/" rel="category tag">Design</a>, <a href="https://www.designsandcode.com/category/development/" rel="category tag">Development</a>, <a href="https://www.designsandcode.com/category/html/" rel="category tag">HTML</a>, <a href="https://www.designsandcode.com/category/javascript/" rel="category tag">JavaScript</a>, <a href="https://www.designsandcode.com/category/php/" rel="category tag">PHP</a>, <a href="https://www.designsandcode.com/category/plugins/" rel="category tag">Plugins</a>, <a href="https://www.designsandcode.com/category/wordpress/" rel="category tag">WordPress</a>.</p>
						
						</header> <!-- end article header -->
					
						<section class="post_content">
						
							<!---->
						
							<p>After a couple of minor set backs we&#8217;re proud to announce the release of Search &amp; Filter Pro. With a ton of new features and a new user interface, Search &amp; Filter Pro makes it easier than ever to allow users to search for content on your WordPress site &#8211; whether this be custom post&#8230;  <a href="https://www.designsandcode.com/720/search-filter-pro-wordpress-plugin/" class="more-link" title="Read Search &#038; Filter Pro for WordPress is out!">Read more &raquo;</a></p>
					
						</section> <!-- end article section -->
						
						<footer>
							
						</footer> <!-- end article footer -->
					
					</article> <!-- end article -->
					
										
										
					<article id="post-598" class="clearfix post-598 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-design category-development category-news" role="article">
						
						<header>
							
							<h3 class="h2"><a href="https://www.designsandcode.com/598/new-site/" rel="bookmark" title="Our new site :)">Our new site :)</a></h3>
							
							<p class="meta">Posted <time datetime="2014-04-10" pubdate>8:06 pm</time> by <a href="https://www.designsandcode.com/author/ross/" title="Posts by Ross" rel="author">Ross</a> <span class="amp">&</span> filed under <a href="https://www.designsandcode.com/category/design/" rel="category tag">Design</a>, <a href="https://www.designsandcode.com/category/development/" rel="category tag">Development</a>, <a href="https://www.designsandcode.com/category/news/" rel="category tag">News</a>.</p>
						
						</header> <!-- end article header -->
					
						<section class="post_content">
						
